<!-- PJG STAG 4702 -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
Regulatory Flexibility Act Analysis 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The FDIC does not believe that adoption of this proposal 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
would have a significant economic impact on a substantial number 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
of small business entities (in this case, small banks), in accord 
