<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</FOOTNOTE>

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
1. Required the filing of a Form 8&hyph;K by any registrant that (a) had furnished a projection to any person, (b) had
reason to believe that its public projections no longer had a reasonable basis, (c) had determined to cease issuing
