V. Solicitation of Public Comment 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The Commission seeks comment on a number of issues. Commenters should discuss both the continuing effectiveness
of the current safe harbors in accomplishing the primary goal of encouraging broader dissemination of forward-looking
