<!-- PJG ITAG l=83 g=1 f=1 -->
J. Possible Alternatives or Supplements to a Safe Harbor 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Commenters also may wish to discuss whether there are alternatives to a safe harbor that would accomplish the same
goal of promoting enhanced disclosure of forward-looking information. For example, are there reforms with regard
to the content and/or presentation of soft information_whether within or outside of Commission filings_that would
