<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
VI. Public Hearings 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The issues addressed in this release have attracted the interest of investors, registrants, analysts and other market
participants, as well as lawyers, accountants, federal legislators and academics. In view of this broad interest,
as well as the importance and complexity of these issues, the Commission intends to authorize public hearings to be
conducted after the close of the comment period. Among other matters, these hearings will explore the assumptions
