<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=4 -->
Federal 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Register
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 (58 FR 63069) temporary regulations under section 4081 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
relating to the imposition of the diesel fuel excise tax for 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
diesel fuel that is removed at a terminal rack, removed from a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
refinery, entered into the United States, or blended outside of 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the bulk/transfer terminal system. Those rules are similar to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the rules relating to the removal, entry, or blending of gasoline under &sect;&sect;48.4081&hyph;2 and 48.4081&hyph;3.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
These proposed regulations generally consolidate the rules 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
relating to gasoline and diesel fuel into a single set of rules 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
applicable to all taxable fuel. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

